le through open access latest one year after published.</span></div><div style=\"font-family: docs-Calibri; font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; text-align: left;\"><br></span></div><div style=\"font-family: docs-Calibri; font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; text-align: left;\">1) Open access requirement for publications</span></div><div style=\"font-family: docs-Calibri; font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">- Funding acknowledgement used is according the funder\'s requiremet. </span></div><font face=\"docs-Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">- Publications deposited into DR-NTU, library will clear with publishers regarding access rights if needed.</span></font></span></div><div><span style=\"text-decoration-skip-ink: none;\"><span style=\"font-family: docs-Calibri; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-skip-ink: none;\"><br></span></span></div><div><span style=\"text-decoration-skip-ink: none;\"><span style=\"font-family: docs-Calibri; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-skip-ink: none;\">2) Please plan your purchases etc. Conciously clear </span><span style=\"font-family: docs-Calibri; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; text-decoration-skip-ink: none;\">all open commitments</span><span style=\"font-family: docs-Calibri; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-skip-ink: none;\"> and ensure all</span><span style=\"font-family: docs-Calibri; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; text-decoration-skip-ink: none;\"> invoices are dated before the project end date. </span></span></div><div><span style=\"text-decoration-skip-ink: none;\"><span style=\"font-family: docs-Calibri; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; text-decoration-skip-ink: none;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; text-align: left; font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></span></div><div><span style=\"text-decoration-skip-ink: none;\"><span style=\"font-family: docs-Calibri; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; text-decoration-skip-ink: none;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; text-align: left; font-weight: 400;\">3) Please ensure all variation needs to reach RSO 4 months before project end date.</span></span></span></div><div><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-family: docs-Calibri; font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: justify;\"><br></span></div><div><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-family: docs-Calibri; font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: justify;\">4) NTU Open Access data sharing</span><span style=\"text-decoration-skip-ink: none;\"><div style=\"font-family: docs-Calibri; font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">- Data related to publications must be made open access by the time the manuscript is published according to NTU Research Data Policy.</span></div><font face=\"docs-Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">- NTU requires PI to deposit their data at DR-NTU-Data  https://researchdata.ntu.edu.sg/</span></font></span></div><div><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-family: docs-Calibri; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br></span></div><div><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-family: docs-Calibri; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Note: This is a system-generated email. </span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-family: docs-Calibri; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Please do not reply to this email</span></div><div><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-family: docs-Calibri; font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br></span></div><div><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-family: docs-Calibri; font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">- Queries on DR-NTU-Data can be emailed to library@ntu.edu.sg</span></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: docs-Calibri; background-color: transparent;\"><br></span></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: docs-Calibri; background-color: transparent;\">Please go to {APPLICATION_URL} to view the details. </span></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: docs-Calibri; background-color: transparent;\"><br></span></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: docs-Calibri; background-color: transparent;\">Thank you.</span></div><div><span style=\"text-decoration-skip-ink: none;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font face=\"docs-Calibri\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br></span></font></div></span></div>','N','Y','quickstart','2020-05-26 14:38:47','fibi_admin',NOW(),'N');
